Rio Tinto to Increase Madagascar Ilmenite Output 64% This Year

-- B y   H a n n a h   M c N e i s h
-- 
2011-02-23T09:25:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-23/rio-tinto-to-increase-madagascar-ilmenite-output-64-this-year.html
  Rio Tinto Plc  plans to increase
production of ilmenite, a mineral used to make white paint, by
64 percent to 473,000 metric tons this year, the company said in
an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
